Hey, i really havent been on moparscape in a while, besides checking in on things, alot of you probobly dont remember me, becuase i have been gone for so long. Ok, well on topic:
First of all, go to ipchicken.com

Then get your name address.
Then you need to enter in this into your webbrowser.(if it doesnt work enter your default gateway)192.168.0.1.
Go to Advanced Setup

Then go to Advanced Port Forwarding

Both port ip range are 43594, and your ip address is your name address from ip chicken

Then just click apply and your done! Easy!
